        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 scroll-animate">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Healthcare</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Patient management, EMR systems, telemedicine platforms</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Finance</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Banking software, payment systems, financial analytics</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Education</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Learning management systems, student portals</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Retail</h3>
